*************** Programming Using BGI **********************

The BGI supplied with Borland's Turbo C compiler can be called
from TopSpeed languages. Header files are supplied (graphics.*)
for each language. If you use #link in your project file, the
relevent library will be included automatically if you include
one of these header files in any compilation in a project.

Note that the BGI can not be used in multi-thread model, as
Borland's drivers are not re-entrant. Large model is recommended.